changelist.name: Changes
changelist.comment:
Simplify dependencies and refactor code documentation
Removed redundant libraries in `requirements.txt` and documented code methods.
Cleaned up unused dependencies to streamline the project setup. Additionally, added detailed docstrings to functions and methods in `exe_tasks.py` and `bAUTOnizer3000.py` for better code maintenance and readability. Adjusted configurations for Python SDK version in `.idea` files.

task.summary:

Enhanced README.md structure, added badges and links, and updated contributing and installation guidelines for better documentation.
